    "üìù Key Backpropagation Concepts:\n",
    "‚Ä¢ Chain Rule: $dL/dw = dL/da √ó da/dz √ó dz/dw$\n",
    "‚Ä¢ Gradients flow backward through the network\n",
    "‚Ä¢ Each layer's gradient depends on the gradient from the next layer\n",
    "‚Ä¢ Weights are updated in the direction that reduces loss"
   ]
